These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, german, italian, brazilian
1. the malaysian is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the german is on the right of the italian##1
3. the malaysian is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | italian | german | malaysian | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, july, december, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Birthday   | may | december | july | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, nurse, project-manager, musician
1. the project-manager is on the left of the electrician##1
2. the nurse is on the left of the musician##1
3. the nurse is on the right of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Job   | project-manager | electrician | nurse | musician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, avocado, cranberry, potato
1. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
2. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Food   | cranberry | apple | avocado | potato |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-5::.
