.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, sports, adventure, disaster
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | adventure | epic | sports |

